{"tid":485066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有睇過套電影-謊言的烙印(The Hunt)","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T15:39:24.000Z","uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8419b2a493878152e7511780a8f9196b9a42d82e","tid":485066,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/232817_a7b39e48b8a66de985c6687aea9706b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F232817_a7b39e48b8a66de985c6687aea9706b1.jpg&h=12614e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《謊言的烙印》故事描述男主角盧卡斯剛經歷離婚事件，好不容易重拾自己生活的腳步，一方面與新女友建立穩定的關係，和10歲的兒子也再建親密的親子之情，同時也找到了幼稚園老師的工作。想要忘卻失婚的痛苦希望回歸正軌的他，卻因為在學校中一個小女孩無心的一句話，讓他的世界整個崩毀，他被冠上性侵的罪名，即使還沒有法律的判罪，但是他卻必須面對整個村子的民眾對他的撻閥。最後即使小女孩改口翻案，但是整個社會與他為敵的氛圍卻沒有改變，大家仍然一意孤行做了最嚴厲的道德審判，令人不寒而慄。"},{"pid":"a5c114401dce2008f0136a7185f156e265b74ed6","tid":485066,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7a8c0e80462aba8b54c43263ce041d9ddcbba0","tid":485066,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-